{
  "texts": [
    "With empirical exploration as the direction, the study aims to provide evidence reference for building effective teaching methods for ChatGPT-like products from the perspective of programming teaching, to promote high-quality development in AIGC-enabled education.",
    "Review of educational applications of artificial intelligence and traditional intelligent conversational Chatbots.",
    "Prior to the emergence of ChatGPT, AI had already been widely applied in education, and various scholars have extensively discussed its empowerment in education from the perspectives of theoretical exploration and system development.",
    "For instance, in the realm of theoretical exploration, researchers have established ethical principles for AI educational applications (Nguyen et al., 2023), methods and models for AI-empowered teaching (Liu et al., 2021), as well as examined the risks and opportunities AI brings to education (Situmorang et al., 2023; Farrokhnia et al., 2023), among others.",
    "At the system development level, a series of AI systems have been developed, such as those guiding novice programmers in learning (Cruz et al., 2017) and assisting teachers in creating programming exercises (Chung et al., 2023)."
  ]
}